title: GET 2 MONTHS FREE!! - Quartz Countertops, Recessed Lighting & More
posting_body: ['Welcome Home to Santa Rosa Oaks!', 'Move into one of our brand new luxury two-bedroom floorplans.', 'Santa Rosa Oaks', 'show contact info', '1521 Range Ave', 'Santa Rosa CA 95401', 'Bed: 2', 'Bath: 1', 'Rent: 2500', 'At Santa Rosa Oaks you won’t just be coming home, you’ll be coming home to a place you love.', 'Life in your Santa Rosa Oaks home also includes high-speed internet that you can easily control from your smart phone.', 'Take a class at Orangetheory Fitness or Crunch Gym.', 'Grab a bite at  one of the many restaurants.', 'There’s even a spa, a nail salon and a beauty salon if you need a little pampering.', 'Or step across the street to enjoy beautiful Finali Park which features two playgrounds, a charming community garden and a spacious dog park.', 'Shop at Whole Foods, Macy’s, Target and many other specialty stores.', 'In addition to our well appointed apartments, our best amenity is our location!', 'We’re just a half-mile down the street from Coddingtown Mall where enjoyment awaits.', 'Our Amenities', 'Gas Range', 'High Speed Internet', 'Disposal', 'Easy Access to Hwy 101 & 12', 'Plank flooring', 'Quartz Countertops', 'Beautifully Landscaped', 'Dishwasher', 'Convenient to Shopping', 'Professional On-Site Management', 'Walk to SMART train & Public Transportation', 'We can’t wait to meet you—contact us today!', 'Located minutes off Highway 101, within walking distance of the SMART Train, and only a short drive to Santa Rosa Junior College and Annadel State Park, Santa Rosa Oaks makes life more convenient and more fun!', 'Come home to a newly renovated community in the heart of Santa Rosa.', 'Our brand new two-bedroom floorplans feature gourmet kitchens with stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops, in-unit washer and dryer, plank flooring, modern finishes and central heating and air.', 'Luxury living in the heart of Sonoma County - beautifully upgraded with luxe finishes.', 'Our community offers brand new, two bedroom floor plans with clean, modern finishes that perfectly compliment our bright, open spaces.']
